node.text: Who caught the @socceraid 2021 match on Saturday? What an epic game! ⚽️ Did you also spot how sharp the teams were looking? We thought you did 😉 @kemcetinay and @primark.man helped dress the players for the big day - take a look behind the scenes at last week's final suit fitting and a closer look at the details. These are dropping SO soon, ready for autumn parties and beyond. Keep your eyes peeled! #PrimarkMan

node.text: While many events have had to be cancelled this year, trans actor, writer and director @jake_graf5 shows us how him and his family are still celebrating Pride at home. Head to primark.com to find out more #Primark #PrideMonth

Make sure you go and check out 'IAmKyami' on Spotfiy for the ultimate soundtrack to match your mood ✨ #Primark #FeelGoodFriday

node.text: This month, we meet the lovely @dani_durrett, an amazing artist with the Boston Ballet. Not only does Daniel's talent shine through, but his determination, positivity and drive to succeed, no matter the obstacle, has got us feeling motivated to go and smash the next goal. Feeling like dance could be for you? Daniel says 'dance is for everyone - just put some music on and let your body do the talking' and we couldn't love that phrase more. Was lovely to meet you, Daniel! Thanks for reminding us to never give up on our goals 🙌 #PrimarkSpotlight
